title: The Beatles - Cinelogue V - Magical Mystery Tour (remaster)
description:
Author: The Beatles
Title: Cinelogue V - Magical Mystery Tour (remastered)
Label: Instant Analysis 
Catalogue #: MM 1028 
Release date: 1975 
Total time: 52:28 
Comments: Double Album.
Source: Laserdisc -> DVD-R -> DVD Audio Extractor -> WAV -> FLAC (level 8)

This double L.P. contained the entire dialogue and music from the film - "Magical Mystery Tour". 
Info link: http://www.jpgr.co.uk/mm1028.html

In the digital age, pieces of this have been released of various bootlegs ("Strawberry Fields", "It&#039;s All In the Mind Y&#039;Know", "Magical Mystical Boy", etc.)  Now we finally have it ALL in one place from the best STEREO mix available.
